Once you've either copied this to a hard drive and unzipped it (if necessary),
there is nothing left to do but play the game and register the product!

To play the game, Just type SAND followed by hitting the [Return] key.
You will be asked two quick questions to optimize performance of Sand Storm.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

You should have all of the following files for the Sand Storm game.

        SAND.EXE   The game.

        SAND.DOC   The documentation.
    REGISTER.DOC   Information regarding registration costs.
      README.DOC   This ubiquitous file.

       SAND1.DAT   Just some important data.
       SAND2.DAT   Just some more important data.
       SAND3.DAT   Even more important data.
       SAND4.DAT   I hope you're not wasting time reading this!
       SAND5.DAT   Last in a distinguished line of data files.

        SAND.SCR   The high scores table.
